## Walker Air Force Base

**Roswell Army Airfield**
Part of [Strategic Air Command](/Strategic_Air_Command)
[Roswell, New Mexico](/Roswell,_New_Mexico)

A 2006 [United States Geological Survey](/United_States_Geological_Survey) aerial photograph offers a bird's-eye view of the sprawling grounds.

